Comment: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:08.30,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Transcendam o espaço e o tempo
Comment: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:19.26,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Vindos de além do futuro, viajando pelo amanhã
Comment: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.03,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Habitem meus sonhos, habitem meu ser
Comment: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:33.80,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Se o relógio continuasse a ticar eternamente
Comment: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:39.94,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Quantos momentos únicos ele testemunharia?
Comment: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:45.50,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Destino! Com estas mãos, nós o agarramos
Comment: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:48.50,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Mesmo esta cidade selvagem
Comment: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.60,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Pode sentir a mudança no ar
Comment: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:51.48,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,É agora!
Comment: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:53.70,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Timeranger, luz da esperança
Comment: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:57.19,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Vocês são como um raio que brilha
Comment: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:02.80,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Sobre esta terra desolada
Comment: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:05.84,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Vindos de milhares de anos, além do futuro
Comment: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.51,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Transcendendo o tempo, viajando pelo amanhã
Comment: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:14.44,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Pessoas do futuro, vivam o "presente"
Comment: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:17.17,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Habitem meus sonhos, habitem meu ser
Comment: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:19.89,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Rumo a um amanhã mais radiante
Comment: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:24.73,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Despertem!
